{"type": "article", "id": 4535, "title": "Polsino 矮凳", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-19T08:06:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233643eBVozpIJurD4mFc7.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t意大利设计师 Alessandro Damin 日前为意大利家居设计品牌 Formabilio 设计了一款名为「Polsino」的矮凳，高度为 45 厘米，凳面直径为 39 厘米。整体造型又呆又萌，底部被做成了挽起的袖口状，搭配以两个标志性的木制纽扣起到了固定的作用，而被卷起的部分恰好能够承担收纳报刊杂志的功能。而米色、灰色的细条纹图案设计也极度贴合衬衫的模样，给人很俏皮的感觉。定价 169 欧元（约合人民币 1294 元），<a href=\"https://www.formabilio.com/shop/sofas/poufs/pouf-design-magazine-holder-polsino\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052336418w4FRPhiupXszarx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233641PLWOX1Qi9SZ5A6MD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233642Gxl4MUBhzj8kHuLZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233642YFucA0RsWS49IGjh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}